Consider two graphs G and H with the following adjacency matrices:

G = \begin{bmatrix}0 & 1 & 1 \\1 & 0 & 0 \\1 & 0 & 0 \\\end{bmatrix}

H = \begin{bmatrix}0 & 1 & 0 \\1 & 0 & 1 \\0 & 1 & 0 \\\end{bmatrix}

Determine whether G and H are isomorphic or not. Provide a detailed explanation of your answer.
